LAGOS – Arik Air is giving its customers a real treat today, Monday, February 14, 2022, which marks this year’s Valentine’s Day. Mr. Adebanji Ola, the airline Spokesman in a statement said that passengers flying Arik Air on the day stand a chance to win complimentary hotel stay (for couples) in selected 5-star hotels in Lagos and Abuja. Additionally, a good number of free return tickets would be won via raffles on the day. BUA Foods Dissociates Self From Artificial Scarcity Of Sugar IHS Partners TechQuest STEM Academy, LASG To Empower 1000… Arik Air is embarking on the Valentine’s Day giveaways as a show of love for its esteemed guests who have supported and trusted the airline over the years. Captain Roy Ilegbodu, Chief Executive Officer of Arik Air, elaborated: “Valentine’s Day is now considered as an occasion to celebrate relationships. At Arik Air we value relationships and this is why we are giving our customers a treat on Valentine’s Day come Monday”. Intending passengers are advised to book their flights online at www.arikair.com or download the Arik mobile app on Google Play or Apps Store.